Moody’s Says Japan 2012 Budget Is Key Factor for Credit Rating

-- B y   T o r u   F u j i o k a
-- 
2011-10-20T09:02:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/moody-s-says-japan-2012-budget-is-key-factor-for-credit-rating.html
Japan ’s budget for next year will be
key for the nation’s credit rating and the country needs
“stability” and “continuity” in its policies,  Thomas Byrne ,
a senior vice president for sovereign risk at Moody’s Investors
Service, said in an interview in  Tokyo  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
